query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('electric-circuits',
'electric-fields',
'energy',
'fluid-dynamics',
'kinematics',
'newtonian-gravity',
'quantum-field-theory',
'reference-frames');
